query.sentence: SELECT SERVER,PROCESSNAME, AVG(DURATION_TIME) AS DURATION_TIME, AVG(WORK_UNITS) AS WORK_UNITS from PM_BTPROCESS WHERE RETURN_CODE IN(1,3) GROUP BY SERVER,PROCESSNAME
SELECT MAX(ORDINAL) AS ORDINAL FROM PM_SCHEDULER WHERE (NOMBREGRUPO = ? OR NOMBREGRUPO = ?) AND (NOMBREHIJO = ? OR NOMBREHIJO = ?)
select GRUPO, DESCRIPCION, FECHA_ALTA_GRUPO from DSP_DEFINICION_GRUPOS where ((GRUPO = ?) OR (-1 = ?)) and TZ_LOCK = 0

SELECT G.TZ_LOCK, G.SALDO_JTS_OID, G.PRIORIDAD, G.USO_SOBREGIRO, G.GRUPO, G.JTS_CTA_DEBITO_COMISION, G.TIPO_SALDO_FONDO, G.PORCENTAJE_FONDO, D.PORCENTAJE_FONDO_UNICO FROM DSP_GRUPOS_CUENTAS G INNER JOIN DSP_DEFINICION_GRUPOS D ON G.GRUPO = D.GRUPO AND G.TZ_LOCK = 0 AND D.TZ_LOCK = 0
WHERE G.GRUPO = ? ORDER BY G.PRIORIDAD

select id_incremental, asiento, sucursal, fecha_proceso from ( select id_incremental, asiento, sucursal, fecha_proceso from CON_ASIENTOS_RELACIONADOS where asiento_origen = ? and sucursal_origen = ? and fecha_proceso_origen = ? and tz_lock = 0 order by id_incremental desc ) where rownum= 1

SELECT PM.GROUP_EXECUTION_ID, PM.EXECUTION_ID, PM.PROCESSNAME, SC.IP_SERVER, SC.HTTP_PORT_SERVER, SC.PROTOCOL, SC.LAST_UPDATE FROM PM_BTPROCESS PM LEFT JOIN SERVERS_CONTROL SC ON PM.SERVER = SC.IP_SERVER WHERE PM.STATE = 'R' ORDER BY PM.EXECUTION_ID
